#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating patterns"
msgstr "Kreiranje novog obrazca"

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:5
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Starting &kapp;"
msgid "Starting &kxstitch;"
msgstr "&kapp; Prirucnik"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:6
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When starting &kapp; you will be presented with a blank canvas of the "
#| "default size. This is also the case when selecting "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice>. The default sizes can be set in the pattern properties "
#| "dialog by enabling the set as default checkbox."
msgid ""
"When starting &kxstitch; you will be presented with a blank canvas of the "
"default size. This is also the case when selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. The default sizes can be set in the pattern properties dialog "
"by enabling the set as default checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Pokretanjem &kapp; pojavit će se prazni zastor u već prethodno podešenoj "
"veličini. To se također pojavljuje pritiskom na: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Podešene veličine mogu biti postavljene u postavke obrasca."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the default size is not suitable for your planned pattern, you can use "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>File Properties</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog to change it. Adjust the values as required "
"and after clicking on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, the pattern will be resized "
"to suit."
msgstr ""
"Ako podešena veličina nije odgovarajuća za kreirani obrazac, možete "
"koristiti  <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Postavke "
"datoteke</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dijalog koji želite izmjeniti. "
"Prilagodite vrijednosti na zahtjevani način i nakon klika na <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton>, obrascu će biti promijenjena veličina tako da odgovara "
"zahtjevima."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before creating a pattern you will need to add some flosses to the palette "
"using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Palette</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Palette "
"Manager</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will enable the tools in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu></menuchoice> menu and toolbar. See the "
"<link linkend=\"PaletteManagerDialog\">Palette Manager Dialog</link> for "
"further information."
msgstr ""
"Prije kreiranja obrasca trebaju se dodati konci paletama koristeći "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Palete</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravitelj paletama</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ovo će onemogućiti alatima u "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</guimenu></menuchoice> meni i alatna traka. "
"Pogledajte <link linkend=\"PaletteManagerDialog\">Upravitelj paletama</link> "
"za još informacija."

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Images"
msgstr "Uvoz raznih formata slike"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:25
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kapp; allows you to import an image. A dialog will be displayed that "
#| "previews the image based on the default import options."
msgid ""
"&kxstitch; allows you to import an image. A dialog will be displayed that "
"previews the image based on the default import options."
msgstr ""
"&kapp; dozvoljava uvoz slike. Pojavljuje se prozor koji daje pregled slike "
"osnovan na defaultnim opcijama uvoza."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The initial size of the pattern will be based on the default pattern size."
msgstr ""
"Inicijalna veličina uzorka će biti zasnovana da podešenu veličinu uzorka."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Options for importing allow you to change the floss scheme used and to limit "
"the number of colors. You can also change the scaling to reduce or enlarge "
"the final pattern."
msgstr ""
"Opcije za uvoz vam mogu omogućiti promjenu končane šeme koja se koristi da "
"se ograniči broj boja. Također možete promijeniti skaliranja za smanjivanje "
"ili povećavanje konačnog uzorka."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Use fractionals</guilabel> checkbox will enable the "
"use of fractional stitches to give more detail for any given pattern size."
msgstr ""
"Označavanjem <guilabel>Koristi razlomke </guilabel> kockica za označavanje "
"ce onemogućiti korištene razlomljenih šavova i davati još detalja za datu "
"veličinu obrasca."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking the <guilabel>Ignore color</guilabel> checkbox will allow the "
"selection of a color within the image which will then be considered as the "
"transparent color and ignored during the import."
msgstr ""
"Provjeravanje  <guilabel>Ignorisanje boje</guilabel> checkbox-a, će vam "
"omogućiti izbor boje za sliku koja će biti razmatrana kao  transparentna "
"boja i zanemarit će se pri uvozu."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the image has been imported, an additional dock window will be "
"available giving a preview of the original image without any color "
"transitions."
msgstr ""
"Nakon što slika biva uvezena, dodatni prozor će davati pregled originalne "
"slike bez promjene boje."

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background Images"
msgstr "Prikaži pozadinske slike"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert an image as a background to the editor window. This is useful "
"if importing the image is not desirable or gives poor results."
msgstr ""
"Sliku možete umetnuti kao pozadinu na prozoru editora. Ovo je korisno ako "
"uvoz slike nije poželjan ili daje loše rezultate."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The image is normally scaled to cover the entire pattern grid. This may not "
"be suitable, therefore you can use the select tool to select an area that "
"you want to cover and then select the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Fit Background Image to Selection</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"This will rescale the image to fit within the selected area. You can "
"continue doing this until you are happy with the result, even after you have "
"started adding stitches."
msgstr ""
"Slika je namještena da prekriva cijelu koordinatnu mrežu obrasca. To može "
"biti nepogodn, stoga možete koristiti alat za odabir područja koje želite "
"pokriti, a zatim odaberite <menuchoice> <guimenu> Pogled </guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem> Prilagodi slike pozadine za odabir </guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Ovo će smanjiti sliku da stane unutar izabrane oblasti. Možete "
"nastaviti raditi ovo sve dok ne budete zadovoljni rezultatom, čak i nakon "
"što ste počeli dodavati šavove."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is no limit to the number of background images that can be added. "
"Although practical limits of the menus will determine how many can be added. "
"The background images are stored within the document, so they will be "
"available when the pattern is reloaded."
msgstr ""
"Ne postoji ograničenje na broj pozadinskih slika koje se mogu dodati. Iako, "
"praktične granice na meniju će odrediti koliko se može dodati pozadinskih "
"slika. Pozadinske slike su pohranjene u dokumentu, tako da će biti na "
"raspolaganju kada obrazac bude ponovo učitan."

#. Tag: title
#: patterns.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pattern Libraries"
msgstr "Patern biblioteka"

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pattern library manager can be used to store patterns for insertion into "
"the working pattern. They can be categorized into a hierarchy of categories "
"and subcategories with multiple root nodes in the library list. The Alphabet "
"tool makes use of these libraries to provide an alphabet of insertable "
"characters that can be assigned an associated key."
msgstr ""
"Upravitelj bibliotekom uzoraka može se koristiti za čuvanje uzoraka koji se "
"koriste za umetanje u radni uzorak. Hijerarhijski se mogu poredati "
"kategorije i potkategorija sa višestrukim korijenskim čvorovima na listi "
"unutar biblioteke. Abecedni alat koristi ove biblioteke da pruže pismu "
"znakove koji se mogu dodijeliti kao odgovarajući ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The library manager is a non modal dialog and can be left open whilst "
"working on your pattern. You can select different libraries as needed and "
"then drag and drop library patterns onto the working pattern."
msgstr ""
"Upravitelj bibliotekama je nemodalni dijalog i može ostati otvoren sve  dok "
"se radi na vašem obrascu. Možete odabrati različite biblioteke po potrebi, a "
"zatim povucite i ispustite biblioteku obrasca na radni obrazac."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding new category headings can be done with a &RMB; on either an existing "
"entry, to create a sub category, or on a blank space on the library list, to "
"create a new root entry, and selecting the <guimenuitem>New Category</"
"guimenuitem> option. Enter the name of the category and click <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Dodavanje novih kategorija proizvoda može da se uradi sa  &RMB; na bilo koji "
"postojeći unos ili na praznom prostor na listi biblioteka, da bi se stvorile "
"podkategorije, potrebno je stvoriti novi korjeni unos, i odabirom "
"<guimenuitem> Nova kategorija </guimenuitem> opciju. Unesite naziv "
"kategorije i kliknite <guibutton> OK </guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating a new library pattern is done by selecting an area of your working "
"pattern, copying and pasting to one of the existing categories."
msgstr ""
"Kreiranje nove biblioteke uzoraka se vrši označavanjem područja radnog "
"obrasca, kopiranje i lijepljenjem u postojeće kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: patterns.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each library pattern has properties, accessed by its context menu. These "
"properties include size, floss scheme, baseline value and associated key. "
"The baseline value is used by the Alphabet tool to adjust the height of a "
"character above, negative values, or below the insertion point. The "
"associated key is again used by the Alphabet tool to match with the key "
"pressed on the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Svaki uzorak biblioteke ima svoje osobine kojima se pristupa putem sadržaja "
"izbornika. Te osobine uključuju veličinu, floss shemu, osnovnu vrijednost i "
"povezane tipke. Osnovnu vrijednost upotrebljava alat za abecedu kako bi se "
"odredila visina gornjih slova, negativne vrijednosti ili ispod tačke unosa. "
"Alat za abecedu upotrebljava i povezanu tipku kako bi se povezao s tipkom "
"koja se pritisne na tastaturi."
